com.paydiant.android.bluetooth.ble

Class BLEScanRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paydiant.android.bluetooth.ble.BLEScanRecord

  • public class BLEScanRecord
extends Object
    Utility class that holds and decodes the advertisement data and scan responses. Raw data will be parsed according to the structures/formats defined in the Core Bluetooth Specification(v.4.1 and later) and Core Specification Supplement(v.4 and later) documents in Bluetooth SIG adopted specifications.
    Since:
    4.9.0.1
    Author:
    Paydiant

      • getServiceUuids

        public List<UUID> getServiceUuids()
        Gets the service UUIDs found within the BLEScanRecord.AdData records. All 16-bit and 32-bit UUIDs will be converted to the 128-bit UUIDs using the following algorithm.

        128_bit_UUID = 16_or_32_bit_UUID * 296 + BASE_UUID
        Returns:
        the list of 128-bit service UUIDs
        Since:
        5.0.0.1

      • isRandomDeviceAddress

        public boolean isRandomDeviceAddress()
        Returns whether the device address returned in getDeviceAddress() is random(true) or public(false) device address.
        Returns:
        true if the device address is a random device address, false if it's a public device address.
        Since:
        5.0.0.1

      • getServiceData

        public Map<UUID,byte[]> getServiceData()
        Returns the service data information for service UUIDs. All the 16-bit and 32-bit service UUIDs will be converted to the 128-bit UUIDs. (See getServiceUuids() for the conversion algorithm)
        Returns:
        a map containing the 128-bit service UUID and its service data
        Since:
        5.0.0.1

      • getCompanyId

        public int getCompanyId()
        Returns the company identifier code found within the BLEScanRecord.AdData records. If not found within AdData records, this will return -1.
        Returns:
        the company identifiers defined in Bluetooth SIG assigned numbers document or -1 if not found within the BLEScanRecord.AdData records.
        Since:
        5.0.0.1
